<seg id="22">In Germany, the procurement of federal public procurement is usually carried out by earthly construction administrations.</seg>
<seg id="23">In the Czech Republic, the responsibility of the state institution for road and railway construction is responsible for entering public procurement in the field of transport infrastructure.</seg>
