<seg id="27">Structure of the Public Procurement Act in both countries</seg>
<seg id="28">In Germany, the course of European procurement proceedings is governed by laws and sublegal standards.</seg>
<seg id="29">The procurement procedure limited only to Germany is governed by budgetary law and relevant administrative acts.</seg>
