<seg id="147">The new legislation contains the following basic provisions: reducing the limits for small-scale orders; the obligation of preliminary notification by the client, including the justification of the order; the prohibition of limiting the number of applicants in a narrower management and cancellation of general possibilities limit the number of applicants by draw; the obligation to publish contracts, including annexes; obligation to publish real and lists of subcontractors.</seg>
<seg id="148">Results of checks related to subsequent phases of procurement procedure</seg>
<seg id="149">Procurement documentation</seg>
<seg id="150">The procurement documents must contain all the information necessary to prepare their offers in a proper form.</seg>
