<seg id="161">Provisions of the German and Czech procurement law</seg>
<seg id="162">Same or similar provisions</seg>
<seg id="163">Both countries have transposed the EU's legal provisions into their national legislation.</seg>
<seg id="164">The basic principle is that the specifications are given generally without reference to a specific product or brand.</seg>
