<seg id="802">Summary evaluation and recommendation</seg>
<seg id="803">Parallel controls of the SAO and BRH were focused on two areas that are essential for the process of procurement of public procurement both in the Czech Republic and in Germany, the application of EU procurement law and corruption prevention.</seg>
