<seg id="7">The submitted joint report informs about the course and result of international cooperation in parallel inspections carried out by the Supreme Audit Office of the Slovak Republic and the Supreme Audit Office of the Czech Republic, focusing on managing excise duty in 2012–2015.</seg>
