<seg id="34">In addition to the main point – exchange of information on the basis of Council Regulation (EC) No 1798/2003 and Commission Regulation (EC) No 1925/2004 – it covered the audit of other topics, such as the registration of payers, VAT tax returns and aggregate reports, which are closely connected with the main point.</seg>
