<seg id="34">The administration of all excise duties in Slovakia performs customs authorities from 1 May 2004, except for excise duty on mineral oil, whose administration performs from 1. 1edna 2002.</seg>
<seg id="35">Until then, the management of excise duties carried out tax authorities.</seg>
