<seg id="151">The conditions of cooperation between the administrative authorities of the Member States competent for the management of excise duty adjusted by 30 June 2005 Council Directive 77/799/EEC, mutual assistance between the competent authorities of the Member States in the area of direct taxes, some excise duty and insurance tax.</seg>
