<seg id="206">The customs authorities in both countries enter all data from the accompanying documents in the register, on the basis of which the transport is implemented.</seg>
<seg id="207">There is currently no uniform electronic system for monitoring the transport of goods in conditional exemption from tax between the European Union Member States, which would allow the administrators of consumer tax in individual Member States to obtain information about the transport of goods in real time.</seg>
<seg id="208">According to the decision of the European Parliament and of the Council of 1152/2003/EC of 16 June 2003, the introduction of an electronic system for monitoring the transport of products subject to excise duty is expected from 1 July 2009.</seg>
