<seg id="218">The establishment of an electronic system for transport and control of goods subject to excise duty in the sense of decision of the European Parliament and of the Council No. 1152/2003/EC will enable electronic transfer of accompanying document and more effective control of movement in conditional liberation mode from tax on the European Union.</seg>
